data.description: Welcome to this beautiful and well-maintained four bedroom, three and a half bathroom, ranch-style home located in the sought after Whitewater High School district. The new owner will appreciate the beautiful hardwood floors throughout the home, the spacious secondary bedrooms, outdoor, enclosed, and temperature-controlled patio, large fenced back yard, and upstairs loft area with a large bedroom (which could be a second master bedroom), full bathroom, and walk-in closet. The sizable kitchen offers plenty of cabinet and counter space as well as an island and stainless steel appliances. The high ceilings throughout add to the appeal of this home. The Maytag washer and dryer will transfer to the new owner. The location of this home is ideal as is close to Pinewood Studios, Hartsfield Jackson Atlanta Airport, and Shopping!
